flowchart TD
    A[Safe Point Sources] --> B1[TSlotState: released/recyclable]
    A --> B2[TContainerState: reset_pending/default_empty]
    A --> B3[TRoundState: closed/completed]
    A --> B4[TReferenceSupplyState: refs invalidated/consumed]
    A --> B5[TDispatchExposureState: exposure closed]
    A --> B6[TBundleAgentState: profile_switch_ready]
    A --> B7[TModeratorState: safe_point_confirmed]

    B1 --> C[Safe Point Evaluator / Policy]
    B2 --> C
    B3 --> C
    B4 --> C
    B5 --> C
    B6 --> C
    B7 --> C

    C --> D{Safe Point Available?}
    D -- No --> E[Block operation + report]
    D -- Yes --> F[Claim safe point]
    F --> G[Execute sensitive operation]
    G --> H[Consume safe point + emit report]

    H --> I[Allowed Operations]
    I --> I1[Container reset]
    I --> I2[Vertical scaling]
    I --> I3[Profile switch]
    I --> I4[Registry rebuild]
    I --> I5[Eviction]
    I --> I6[Reference invalidation]
